கடுமை.note. in most of its meanings  
bad or injurious qualities are implied. it differs from கடு மை  
in several meanings. like that and similar abstract nouns  
it drops the ter mination and combines with other nouns as an adjective  
according to rule. வறுமைகொடிது. poverty is cruel. வயிற்றுக்கொடுமையினால்வருந்துகிறான். he is vexed by want of food  
